      <odd id="aspace_475b595bee0c653c3ce0b8220f3f7ced">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 5-G (YRG 5-G), Records documenting personnel services at Yale University.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_ca91cc2517672af395419436e705a2ba">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Labor-Management Relations office, 2005.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
